dc_description_s: 2 maps on 1 sheet ; sheet 45 x 54 cm|Relief shown pictorially.|North oriented to the top on top map; north oriented to the top right corner on bottom map.|Shows the northern Rhine from Gorinchem, Netherlands to Wesel, Germany.|Does not match any states listed in Van der Krogt.|Copy differs only slightly from Van der Krogt's 3705:1.1 in that the wording in the publishing credit varies.|From the Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan.
